Package net.tfobz.vocabletrainer.data

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    VocableTrainerIO
    This class handles the import and export of flashcard data for the Vocable Trainer application.
    VocableTrainerLocalization
    Handles localization for the Vocable Trainer application by loading language-specific strings from YAML files and mapping them to application constants.
    VocableTrainerRunSettings
    This class manages the settings for running a session of the Vocable Trainer.
    VocableTrainerSettingsIO
    Class responsible for handling the settings of the Vocable Trainer application, including loading, saving, and managing default settings.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    VocableTrainerLocalization.localisation
    Supported localizations for the application.
    VocableTrainerRunSettings.TimeUnit
    Enumeration representing the time unit options for setting limits.
